  "response": "As of the latest data up to October 2023, several excellent Android phones are available above the \u20b935,000 price point in India. The best choice can vary depending on your specific needs and preferences, such as camera quality, performance, battery life, or software experience. Here are some of the top contenders:\n\n1. **Samsung Galaxy S21 FE** - Offers great performance, high-quality cameras, and a smooth user experience.\n2. **Google Pixel 6** - Known for its exceptional camera capabilities, clean software experience, and timely updates.\n3. **OnePlus 10T** - Features powerful hardware, fast charging, and a smooth software experience with OxygenOS.\n4. **Xiaomi 12 Pro** - Strong performance, excellent display, and premium build quality.\n5. **Samsung Galaxy S22** - Outstanding camera system, premium design, and powerful performance.\n6. **Asus ROG Phone 6** - Best choice for gamers with its high-end specs, gaming features, and robust build.\n\nEach of these phones has its strengths, so it\u2019s essential to consider what matters most to you in a smartphone. If you prioritize camera quality, the Google Pixel 6 might be the best choice. For gaming, the Asus ROG Phone 6 could be ideal. For overall performance and a balanced experience, the Samsung Galaxy S22 is a strong contender.",
